name: history_scottish-witchcraft
title: Scottish Witchcraft
description:
Find out what it took to be accused of witchcraft

This database contains a variety of information on the almost 4,000 people who were accused of practicing witchcraft between 1563 and 1736 in Scotland.

![Witchcraft accusations](https://cdn.filepicker.io/api/file/hUgRraUoT9aph8idkQWe "Witchcraft accusations") Chart by [@nrippner](https://data.world/nrippner)
